trans-unit.source: An instance of a ObjectListShowCommandsEventArgs object is automatically created and passed to the event handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.ShowItemCommands> event of an <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList>.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância de um objeto ObjectListShowCommandsEventArgs é automaticamente criada e passada para o manipulador de eventos para o <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.ShowItemCommands>evento de <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList>.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.ShowItemCommands>

trans-unit.source: An inherited class or event handler can use this event to show commands unique to the item, by changing the collection of commands in the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.Commands%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Um manipulador de eventos ou classe herdado pode usar esse evento para mostrar os comandos exclusivo para o item, alterando o conjunto de comandos no <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.Commands%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.Commands%2A>
